Introduction

3RACHA is a hip-hop trio and sub-unit of the K-pop group Stray Kids under JYP Entertainment. The group consists of CB97 (Bang Chan), SPEARB (Changbin), and J.ONE (Han), who are also the main producers and songwriters of Stray Kids.

Even before Stray Kids was officially formed, the group was known to release music on SoundCloud.
